        "id": "69e006d51511c22199e24f9d",
        "title": "DDoS Attack Detected",
        "description": "",
        "remediation_steps": "1. Activate DDoS mitigation rules at network edge immediately\n2. Block source IP at firewall\n3. Enable rate limiting on affected game server\n4. Notify game server team to expect degraded performance\n5. Monitor traffic_mbps field to track attack intensity\n6. Consider enabling CDN or DDoS protection service (e.g. Cloudflare)\n7. Document attack timeline for post-incident review",
